<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink323">
<l>vaḷḷeyiṟṟuc cennāy vayavuṟu piṇaviṟkuk</l>
<l>kaḷḷiyaṅ kaṭattiṭaik kēḻal pārkkum</l>
<l>veñcurak kavalai nīnti</l>
<l>vanta neñcanī nayantōḷ paṇpē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O heart that has come, passing through forked paths</l>
<l>in the hot wasteland,</l>
<l>where in the pretty forest of Kaḷḷi trees a wild dog with sharp teeth </l>
<l>watches out for a boar [to hunt] for its pregnant mate! </l>
<l>The girl you long for is good-natured.  </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
